	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Why is this resistor on the carts?  I'm making my own cart and I'm using the MAX795 ic for battery control. I'm wondering if I need that resistor too or not....<br /><br />Thanks guys for you help. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

